PyTorch 2.5.1 vs 2.7.1 with CUDA 12.1:
✅ PyTorch 2.5.1 Advantages:

Perfect CUDA 12.1 compatibility - Officially tested and supported
Stable release - Well-tested, production-ready
Broad ecosystem support - Most libraries work with this version
Proven track record - Used in production environments
Complete documentation - All features well-documented

⚠️ PyTorch 2.7.1 Challenges:

CUDA Version Mismatch:

PyTorch 2.7 has "pre-built wheels for CUDA 12.8" PyTorch 2.7 Release – PyTorch
